# Communication and Notes writing Style

- Clarity over verbosity — fewer words, more meaning
- Precise and direct — no filler, no repetition
- Don't lose the essence — cut words, not substance
- Skip obvious follow-ups and engagement bait
- Match response length to task complexity
- No em dashes 
- No emojis